<div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; funcon getFinalGemaScore(s) {</div>
<div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; const allScores = Object.values(s);</div>
<div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; if (s.ga === 0) return { level: 0, tle: "0 - Blind",
descripon: "Gender was not considered in the analysis." };</div>
<div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; const isTransformave = s.ga === 3 &amp;&amp;
s.use === 3 &amp;&amp; s.power === 3 &amp;&amp; (s.interseconality === 3 || s.stakeholder === 3)
&amp;&amp; !allScores.includes(0) &amp;&amp; !allScores.includes(1);</div>
<div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; if (isTransformave) return { level: 3, tle: "3 -
Transformave", descripon: "Project is designed to be gender transformave." };</div>
<div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; const scoresGte2 = allScores.lter(score =&gt; score
&gt;= 2).length;</div>
<div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; const isResponsive = s.ga &gt;= 2 &amp;&amp; s.use
&gt;= 2 &amp;&amp; s.power &gt;= 1 &amp;&amp; scoresGte2 &gt;= 3 &amp;&amp;
!allScores.includes(0);</div>
<div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; if (isResponsive) return { level: 2, tle: "2 -
Responsive", descripon: "Project is designed to be gender responsive." };</div>
<div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; if (s.ga &gt;= 1) return { level: 1, tle: "1 - Aware",
descripon: "Project is gender aware but does not meet higher criteria." };</div>
<div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; return { level: 0, tle: "0 - Blind", descripon:
"Scoring did not meet minimum criteria." };</div>
<div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; }</div>
